      "content": "# This check validates required environment decisions before running a deployment script.\nimport os, sys\n\nrequired = [\"PROJECT_ENDPOINT\", \"MODEL_DEPLOYMENT_NAME\", \"MCP_SERVER_URL\", \"MCP_ALLOWED_TOOLS\"]\nmissing = [name for name in required if not os.environ.get(name)]\nif missing:\n    sys.exit(f\"Missing required settings: {', '.join(missing)}\")\n\nallowed = [t.strip() for t in os.environ[\"MCP_ALLOWED_TOOLS\"].split(\",\") if t.strip()]\nif not allowed:\n    sys.exit(\"MCP_ALLOWED_TOOLS must name at least one tool.\")\nif any(t == \"*\" for t in allowed):\n    sys.exit(\"Wildcard MCP tools are not allowed for production.\")\n\nprint(\"Preflight passed for MCP agent deployment settings.\")\n"
