     "definition": "The official Azure MCP Server lives in microsoft/mcp after Azure/azure-mcp was archived. Its Kusto area is titled Azure Data Explorer and registers read-only commands for sample, query, cluster list, cluster get, database list, table list, and table schema. In consolidated mode it is described as getting Azure Data Explorer Kusto details: list clusters, execute KQL queries, manage databases, explore table schemas, and get data samples.",
