     "mentalModel": "Use the official Azure MCP Server first when you need broad Azure integration and maintained Kusto tooling. Expose only the Kusto namespace or a narrow allow-list when the lesson is about read-only ADX questions.",
     "diagram": "flowchart LR\n  Agent[Foundry agent] --> MCP[Azure MCP Server]\n  MCP --> ToolList[Kusto tools]\n  ToolList --> Cluster[List clusters]\n  ToolList --> Schema[Get schema]\n  ToolList --> Query[Run KQL]\n  Query --> ADX[Azure Data Explorer]",
