      "content": "# Azure DevOps creates work items with JSON Patch operations.\n# This example is representative and safe because it only builds a payload.\npatch = [\n    {'op': 'add', 'path': '/fields/System.Title', 'value': 'Teach ADO MCP connector'},\n    {'op': 'add', 'path': '/fields/System.Description', 'value': 'Create beginner friendly lesson content.'},\n    {'op': 'add', 'path': '/fields/System.Tags', 'value': 'foundry; mcp; ado'},\n]\nprint(patch)\n"
